title: Dell PowerVault ME5: Disks
agents: dell_powervault_me5
catalog: hw/storagehw/dell
license: GPLv2
distribution: Sher Zaman
description:
 Monitors the physical disks of a Dell PowerVault ME5 system: disk health,
 error and drive-down conditions and SMART status. Temperature, remaining SSD
 life and power-on hours are reported where the disk provides them, with
 optional lower levels on remaining SSD life (off by default).

 State is taken from the disk health value reported by the array. Conditions
 are configurable via the "Dell PowerVault ME5 disk" ruleset.

item:
 The disk location (for example {"0.0"}).

discovery:
 One service is created per disk.
